{"tid":717220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB: 美國財長表示限制中国投資美國高科技係fake news","createTime":"2018-06-26T00:52:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T02:58:06.000Z","uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"7c170febe3e5177c7ae82836f7ccec0d5e0f90fb","tid":717220,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T00:52:07.000Z","msg":"講啲唔講啲，淨係拎fake news呢句無限loop <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美財長：限制投資美敏感科技業非只針對中國<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/5641/3218481\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5641%2F3218481&d=QngSKzRB433w1rxS1sxLd26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=3e217f87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/5641/3218481</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">美國財政部長梅努欽今天表示，財政部將公布的限制投資美國敏感科技業的規定並非只針對中國，而將適用「所有想要竊取我國技術的國家」。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報導，梅努欽（Steven Mnuchin）在推特貼文說，彭博（Bloomberg）和「華爾街日報」（WallStreet Journal）兩家媒體有關限制投資的報導「是不正確的，是假新聞」。<br />\n</span><br />\n華爾街日報昨天報導，美國財政部正在研擬法規，禁止中資持股至少25%的企業收購擁有「工業重要技術」的美國企業。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">報導引述熟知內情的消息人士說，國家安全會議（NSC）和商務部（Commerce Department）已開始研擬「加強」出口管制的計畫，以防工業重要技術落入中國之手。</span><br />\n<br />\n彭博也報導，美國財政部正考慮援引一項緊急法律，加強審查中國在美投資敏感技術，恐使美中爆發無可逆轉的貿易戰。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士說，1977年生效的「國際緊急經濟權力法」（International Emergency Economic Powers Act）將鎖定未來的潛在投資，意味現已存在的投資不會受到影響。<br />\n<br />\nTreasury Secretary Mnuchin says investment restrictions will apply to 'all countries that are trying to steal our technology'<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2018/06/25/treasury-secretary-mnuchin-says-investment-restrictions-will-apply-to-.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2Ftreasury-secretary-mnuchin-says-investment-restrictions-will-apply-to-.html&d=QngSKzRB433w1rxS1sxLd26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=df13ef7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2018/06/25/treasury-secretary-mnuchin-says-investment-restrictions-will-apply-to-.html</a><br />\n<br />\nTreasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin said Monday that a forthcoming statement from the government related to reports of investment restrictions will apply to China and other countries that threaten U.S. intellectual property rights on technology.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;On behalf of @realDonaldTrump, the stories on investment restrictions in Bloomberg &amp; WSJ are false, fake news. The leaker either doesn&rsquo;t exist or know the subject very well. <span style=\"color: red;\">Statement will be out not specific to China, but to all countries that are trying to steal our technology,&quot; Mnuchin said in a tweet.</span>"},{"pid":"a1554c41063a640b35eaf756b73b3d8ab11786d1","tid":717220,"uid":14918,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T00:53:13.000Z","msg":"偷換概念既極致"},{"pid":"829eeeec3e2f161ca0ffce0a0c6447cbe1a4a990","tid":717220,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T01:12:52.000Z","msg":"不要問，只要j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529681903ae8c7bcd213f38b43f5222546652101","tid":717220,"uid":58552,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T01:13:41.000Z","msg":"Cctvb 真fake news"},{"pid":"a7028d9872d553c79fb4165015094e93fed57b18","tid":717220,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T01:14:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f9cab3ec53b6e466e6e964c559d6ccda97a9e3c","tid":717220,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1554c41063a640b35eaf756b73b3d8ab11786d1","tid":717220,"uid":14918,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":